title: Malaysia Industrial Production MoM
description: Industrial Production in Malaysia increased 3 percent in November of 2021 over the previous month. Industrial Production Mom in Malaysia averaged 0.39 percent from 2009 until 2021, reaching an all time high of 25.90 percent in June of 2020 and a record low of -27.10 percent in April of 2020. This page provides - Malaysia Industrial Production MoM - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Department of Statistics, Malaysia
